Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:04.48,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.87,0:00:07.33,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a week since the \Nbattle in the coal pit,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.20,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:18.51,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,and my shield's gained so many\Nskills and abilities I lost count of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:14.66,sign_336_5_Animal_Needle_Sh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,521)}Animal Needle Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.27,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,But I still let my guard down and got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:27.38,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:30.43,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:42.11,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,The Wave is almost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:45.52,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time we upgraded our equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:46.92,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:48.94,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:10.34,sign_3370_33_The_Rising_of_th,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,645)}The Rising of the Shield Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:25.79,sign_6970_33_Walking_Over_Cor,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(438,596)}Wave of Catastrophe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:24.51,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I hardly recognized you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.57,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,You've turned into a real pretty lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:32.87,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:34.08,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,What've you been up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:36.89,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I had the innkeeper teach me table manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:40.52,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat my food properly,\Nlike Naofumi-sama does.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:41.84,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:43.67,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:45.59,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like the pipsqueak you used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:49.05,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:51.85,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:55.02,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's hard to please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:57.45,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually quite shocked, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:00.23,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This country is full of lolicons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:03.98,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Miss. You're adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:05.77,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Have another one on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:08.96,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand finding \Nlittle girls cute, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.64,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:13.15,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:15.86,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You people take it too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.92,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Say, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:21.76,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know what demi-humans are like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:22.75,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:24.18,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:27.06,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to buy armor for Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:29.39,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any recommendations?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:31.73,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're here for {\i1}your{\i0} equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:34.89,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:37.52,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,but think about yourself first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:40.74,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget how you just \Ngot hurt in the plains?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:43.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,No, but you need a weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.25,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:47.04,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You'd best stop messing around,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:49.99,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,or you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:55.46,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! This sword seems really sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.96,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,It's magic iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.59,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna try it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.41,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Will you give us a discount?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:03.60,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Anything for you, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:05.90,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:08.71,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,While we're at it, could you \Nshow us some armor, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:10.01,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.85,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,She stands up for herself now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:15.16,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe she's just rude...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:18.88,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Our budget is around 180 silvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:20.11,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.82,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:26.85,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's my style...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.50,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:32.28,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it will strip Naofumi-sama \Nof all his individuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:36.41,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can whip up something made to order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:37.86,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Made to order?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:38.59,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:41.87,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind me using materials\NI've got on hand, I can finish by tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:43.83,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:48.12,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It was so nice of him to give us a\Ndiscount on that sword, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:49.25,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:53.47,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,He's a really nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:55.44,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:59.00,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.15,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:01.91,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get the cheapest lunch set you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:06.42,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,and she'll have the kids' lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:10.30,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama! I'm not a kid anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:12.67,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get the cheapest lunch set, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:14.79,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:17.43,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't need to \Nforce yourself to act grown-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.62,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not forcing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:24.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this make me\N look like a typical villain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:26.30,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,So cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:29.00,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It suits you perfectly! You look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.84,top,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,I call it the Barbarian Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:37.48,sign_9509_88_Wave_of_Catastro,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Barbarian Armor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.55,top,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,You're rocking it, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.93,top,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a real bandit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:37.47,top,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to be a hero, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:38.99,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You look so dashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:41.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you did make it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.99,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a shame not to wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:58.94,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,The whole town is on edge now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:01.17,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The Wave is nearly here, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:04.61,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If only I knew when and where it'll start,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:06.39,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I could come up with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:09.84,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Has nobody told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:15.19,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,You know that church you \Ncan see from the town square?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.08,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,There's a huge hourglass inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:21.66,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,When the last grain of sand in it falls,\N the heroes and their parties
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:24.41,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,will be sent to where the \NWave begins, or so I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:29.38,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,Come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:40.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the dragon hourglass \Nthe king was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:52.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's counting down to the Wave?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.87,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Naofumi I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:06:59.86,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:03.31,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You're still fighting with \Nsuch flimsy equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:07.44,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they, Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:14.82,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Motoyasu-sama's talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:20.89,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:25.11,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kitamura Motoyasu, the Spear Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:27.09,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.48,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:32.15,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu-sama, why are you \Ncomplimenting a filthy demi-human?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:36.14,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,A girl as adorable as you \Nshouldn't wield a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.01,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:43.91,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:46.81,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I've sworn to fight with Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:48.14,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,With Naofumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:49.80,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:52.10,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay with him, you'll be in danger—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:54.74,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.67,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Am I not right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:01.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:06.61,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you've heard the \Nrumors about him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.05,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,Rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:16.81,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,See you at the Wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:18.81,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold us back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:33.57,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:34.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:38.49,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen between \Nyou and the other heroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:43.75,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:45.58,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:51.59,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go ahead and turn in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:53.97,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:09:00.43,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I tell the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:03.15,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,nobody believes me, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:10.90,sign_9509_88_Wave_of_Catastro,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(107,1)}The Day of the Wave of Catastrophe
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.86,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:18.38,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:26.54,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just want to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:32.42,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly grateful I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:38.94,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You cured my illness and fed me warm meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:43.71,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me how to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.31,flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents won't ever come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:51.04,flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,But we can prevent other kids \Nfrom going through what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:10:00.66,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,And you gave me a reason to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:03.46,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,A reason to fight the Waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:08.49,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I am your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:13.91,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever you go, I will go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:17.17,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:45.27,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:49.24,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:55.41,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The Wave of Catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:15.42,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys... Raphtalia, we're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:16.94,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Look there, Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.43,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's the village of Lute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.16,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Have the villagers evacuated?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.41,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,A flare?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:30.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,They think their job's done once they let\Nthe knights know where they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:34.94,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,The castle isn't far away, but by \Nthe time the knights get here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:36.46,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,the village will be wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:39.12,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,To Lute Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:41.63,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:54.56,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia, go help the villagers evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:01.13,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.91,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:04.99,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lure the enemy away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:17.29,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,One of the heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:20.32,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,The Shield Hero is here for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:23.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:25.12,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep them occupied!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:26.51,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here while you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.43,top,V,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:31.94,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:34.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.61,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:38.35,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.73,top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:44.52,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.12,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This way, you stupid zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:00.67,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up with me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:06.92,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I risking my life to \Ndefend total strangers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:12.03,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:15.73,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Come this way, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:17.71,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:34.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,There's way too many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:36.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,How can I minimize the damage to the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:47.00,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:48.32,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:55.02,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,No... Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.31,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.51,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's showing no signs of slowing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:05.27,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What are those guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:06.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.91,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:59.41,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you come back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:04.12,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,We all changed our minds after seeing \Nhow courageously you're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:06.91,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,This village is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:09.42,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot run away and abandon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:12.22,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.60,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:17.21,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Help me keep the enemy pinned down \Nuntil the evacuation's complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:25.82,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Die, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:33.60,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can't deal with this one!\NFall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:35.48,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:37.29,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Think about your families!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die here for no reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.20,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:42.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:45.00,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:52.92,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:54.79,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:57.89,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We'll handle things here. \NHurry up and evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:58.97,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:00.93,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Please be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:04.55,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:08.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's numbers aren't going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.29,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:15.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:18.28,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.77,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,We burned them all to death at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:41.97,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,The Shield Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.62,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:47.43,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Tch. They didn't care that we were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:55.15,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do this knowing \NNaofumi-sama was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:57.20,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on your answer, \NI'll have your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:16:58.61,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Draw your swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:02.32,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Are you with the Shield Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.37,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I am Naofumi-sama's sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:06.08,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,None may disrespect him in my presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:10.51,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can point your blade at the \Nroyal knights, you damned demi-human?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:14.37,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of knight neglects the \Npeople he's meant to defend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:16.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.12,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:19.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.71,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:22.48,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,So long as you behave yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:24.76,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,we won't be forced to make any mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:26.97,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:32.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I could sit tight and watch you \Nmorons become monster feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:34.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't sound too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:39.62,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't falter! Get in formation...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:43.77,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Want to die an honorable death in battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:44.70,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:45.56,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:53.51,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Listen here! We'll buy you time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:55.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Use it to get in formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:59.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:00.01,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.57,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Let the Shield handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:19.18,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading to where the Three Heroes are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.50,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:30.34,main,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Support the Shield Hero!\NPhalanx formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:34.35,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Phalanx!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:35.25,main,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:40.60,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama, look at the knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:43.33,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Forget them. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.65,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:50.43,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.60,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:55.56,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:58.81,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:04.59,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama... Look at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:13.09,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Walk in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:15.38,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,This boss was a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:18.54,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. The next Wave will \Nprobably be easy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:21.26,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's Naofumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:23.37,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,It's good that he wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:25.62,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,He'd just hold us back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.59,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:29.22,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:33.47,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:35.19,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,The knights, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.41,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit late to show up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:39.07,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:41.91,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:44.91,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,His Highness has rewards for each of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:47.26,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:15.31,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:20.19,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I killed all the monsters \Nleft in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:22.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:24.76,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Did we...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:27.39,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,...win?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:30.97,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:35.46,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:41.29,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't have made it without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:45.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Thank your lucky stars, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:46.76,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:51.84,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Your presence is what helped us survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:55.23,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never forget what you've done for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.61,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:07.78,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,They looked truly grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:10.73,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:19.27,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We prevented at least a few kids from \Ngoing through what I did, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:21.70,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:23.65,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:27.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:31.71,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I killed lots of monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:33.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
